rComments: This guy is awesome. He is clearly enthusiastic about math, and his lectures and clear and funny. He is always available to answer questions, and is super helpful during office hours. I 100% recommend taking any of his classes.

One of the best profs I ever had. He truly loves math and the lectures were awesome. He cares a lot about his students and is very accessible outside class, he helped me with problems by email. Now, be prepared to work. Also, he may be a little impatient with futile things (like speaking in class or not stapling assignments).
